  <summary date="2019-02-25T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Presidential Pardon Transparency Act of 2019

This bill requires certain information about presidential pardons and reprieves to be made public.

Specifically, the President must publish the issue date, recipient, and full text of each pardon or reprieve granted.</summary>
